### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### MCP Initialize
POST http://localhost:5000/mcp/sse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "test-client",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

### MCP Tools List
POST http://localhost:5000/mcp/sse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### Test Connection (火山引擎)
POST http://localhost:5000/mcp/sse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "test_connection",
    "arguments": {
      "vendor": "huoshan"
    }
  }
}

### List Voices (火山引擎)
POST http://localhost:5000/mcp/sse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 4,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "list_voices",
    "arguments": {
      "vendor": "huoshan"
    }
  }
}

### Generate TTS (火山引擎)
POST http://localhost:5000/mcp/sse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "generate_tts",
    "arguments": {
      "vendor": "huoshan",
      "voice_id": "zh_female_wenrouxiaoya_moon_bigtts",
      "text": "你好，这是一个测试。",
      "speed": 1.0
    }
  }
}
